name: Magislayer Guardian - Jeanne D'arc
effect:
2 Level 4 "Magislayer" Monsters
This card can only be Xyz Summoned OR Special Summoned by an "Magislay" or "Magikill" card effect, and can't be Summoned by other ways. You can only Special Summon 1 "Magislayer Guardian - Jeanne D'arc" per turn. You can Special Summon this card from your Extra Deck by sending 2 Spell/Traps you control to the GY. Once while this card is face-up on the Field, If this card was Special Summoned on this turn and has no Materials (Quick Effect): You can attach up to 2 Spell/Traps from your GY to this card as Xyz Materials, this effect cannot be negated. If this card is Special Summoned; You can target 1 "Magislayer" Monster in your GY: If you want you can detach 2 Xyz Materials from this card, regardless that Special Summon the targeted Monster from your GY, but if you don't detach any materials of this card, banish this card afterward. (Quick Effect): You can return this card you control to the Extra Deck and if you do, you can Special Summon 1 non-Xyz "Magislayer" Monster from your Extra Deck. You can only activate this effect of "Magislayer Guardian - Jeanne D'arc" once per turn.
